channel.title: What next for my new line of servers? Project Tribulation (omfg now WAI) JOIN!
channel.description:
Well guys as most of you know, I released HBG-Scape V4 and I will be making no more HBG-Scape's so... time to move on!
I am starting...
[size=20pt]PROJECT TRIBULATION[/size]
Things I want this server to have:
Full Range Full mage (Lunar spells included) All skills working Commands to switch mage, ::normal ::ancient ::lunar Full runecrafting with abyss to get to alters... Defence bonus working Item requirements to wield All silab items equipping correctly with stats set Portal room Home in unique area Jad minigame Godsword minigame (not gsmini) Barrows working with dig on hills to get inside, and then click on tomb to make the spawn All barrows effects working working prayer Unique pk area Clan wars working Clan chat working Veng working Skillcape emotes some other stuff will be added later....
People I need:
Coders: 3 - 5 - Hah Bah Gee - Killer75230 - - -
Jr. Coders (people that are here to learn mainly): as many that wanna sign up... - azza123 - - - - -
Hoster: 24/7 -
A Person to have remote desktop set up (possibly me) -
Idea men: 2 of them - Adog17x -
Please sign up today! Use the following format:
[code] Name: Position you want: Reason you want it: Why you think you will be good at it: Experience you have: Proof: Msn: [/code]
This will be a great source and a reveloution in private servers, JOIN TODAY!
